{"tid":2090571,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"改變抗爭口號 支持一國一制","createTime":"2020-07-02T08:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T16:37:48.000Z","uid":37038,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5b5f3ad5a55665117a51f19fd51eb0484e07fd5f","tid":2090571,"uid":37038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:36:36.000Z","msg":"大陸講堅定維持一國兩制,<br />\n係因為中共用一國兩制攞左太多著數,<br />\n根本香港已經俾大陸陰乾.<br />\n<br />\n大家要認清一國兩制對中共好重要,<br />\n所以我地更加要打破一國兩制.<br />\n<br />\n我唔係叫大家反對一國兩制,<br />\n係叫大家支持一國一制,<br />\n我地要問中共既然國家制度咁好, <br />\n點解香港唔用國家制度,<br />\n點解仲要一國兩制？<br />\n<br />\n仲口口聲聲話堅定維持一個國家兩個制度,<br />\n咁係唔係想分裂國家？<br />\n一國就一國, 你講咩兩個制度.<br />\n<br />\n大家要改變抗爭口號,<br />\n我地要一國一制, 唔要一國兩制."},{"pid":"72ce52c488920cf743b7814d5a12fb6cc02c9860","tid":2090571,"uid":354581,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:38:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YTSx6VQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYTSx6VQ.png&h=9a60d76d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請你小心言論！"},{"pid":"5d51d05f9727e041aef290084cc6ae0f74962be1","tid":2090571,"uid":37038,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72ce52c488920cf743b7814d5a12fb6cc02c9860","tid":2090571,"uid":354581,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:38:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YTSx6VQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYTSx6VQ.png&h=9a60d76d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請你小心言論！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:44:30.000Z","msg":"我叫人支持中國大一統"},{"pid":"9ee622fc67ee9d4f5cc11e1bc04bab7c9c3cf5af","tid":2090571,"uid":37038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d51d05f9727e041aef290084cc6ae0f74962be1","tid":2090571,"uid":37038,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72ce52c488920cf743b7814d5a12fb6cc02c9860","tid":2090571,"uid":354581,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:38:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\